Description_lang: Blackhand throws his hammer at the ceiling, causing Demolition and  Massive Demolition to occur. Demolition inflicts $156497s1 Physical damage to all enemies within $156497A1 yards. The damage inflicted is decreases the farther away an enemy is from the impact point.
AuraDescription_lang: Blackhand throws his hammer at the ceiling, causing debris to fall. Demolition inflicts $156497s1 Physical damage to all enemies within $156497A1 yards and Massive Demolition inflicts $156479s1 Physical damage to all enemies. The damage inflicted by both is decreases the farther away an enemy is from the impact point.
